{"tid":2440012,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"SONY新款PS5曝光 升级5nm處理器、2023年登場","createTime":"2021-03-09T15:49:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T09:06:26.000Z","uid":32577,"like":7,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"fd0a8f5f822ece204ea246bc2c0fa03ccc9fad42","tid":2440012,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:49:46.000Z","msg":"SONY PS5破天荒地首發了兩個版本，但除了有無光碟機，核心規格幾乎相同。<br />\n<br />\n考量到競爭對手Xbox Series S有著更便宜的售價及PS5居高不下的人氣，我們有理由相信PS5的中期改款，如：PS5 Slim、PS5 Pro。<br />\n關於PS5 Slim，有進一步的情報出現。據爆料者透露，PS5 Slim規劃2023年量產，核心晶片升級至台積電5nm製程。當年，PS4首發時採用的是AMD客製的28nm晶片，之後於PS4 Slim與PS4 Pro上升級至16nm。<br />\n<br />\nPS5 Slim的功耗將更低，同時機身設計更加輕薄，畢竟PS5是目前體積最大的遊戲機，一些電視櫃表示有苦難言。<br />\n<br />\n歷史上，PS3、PS4的改款機種皆於第一代首發三年後，PS2則是等了四年時間。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/APepfZv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAPepfZv.png&h=e276f313&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8e229283e31ecbde3c6f829309afa190e1600fb","tid":2440012,"uid":32577,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 買到當你羸"},{"pid":"49b1c4d6df32bfdbdae28c62e77cf7fb09ec0497","tid":2440012,"uid":38904,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:51:05.000Z","msg":"升<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>级</strong></span></span>5nm處理器、2023年登場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb28467174aeb226502d8711fb8fa6ad60cb54b2","tid":2440012,"uid":48212,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:51:08.000Z","msg":"到時第一版都未撚買到呀 屌你sony"},{"pid":"74e8f6814b3e23015dff01cfe1fc47aa3a204074","tid":2440012,"uid":5490,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:51:47.000Z","msg":"改左個手掣先啦屌你老母<img